title: ScribdViewer 1.1 by Synaps3 - PDF Blocked Scribd
description:
This program will allow you to view blocked documents on scribd without
paying. To use, simply copy a URL and paste into the ScribdViewer.exe.
If you would like to use the built-in viewer (allows for printing PDFs),
then you will need the ActiveX (Internet Explorer) version of flash
player and a PDF printer program. These are both included in the Extra
folder. If you only want to view the documents, you can just copy the
link generated by ScribdViewer.exe into your browser. If you try to
print from firefox, it will result in the flashplayer plugin crashing,
so you need to use the built-in viewer.

Settings.inf contains some brief info on how to generate the links from
scribd. This may need to be updated periodically. I've included this to
reduce the need for regular program updates.

Programmed by: Synaps3
